timing_derate_..._additive_mode(25.10)  timing_derate_..._additive_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_derate_incremental_adjust_additive_mode

Syntax
       timing_derate_incremental_adjust_additive_mode

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Allows  the software to accumulate incremental derate values instead of
       overwriting them.

       When set to false, the successive application of  incremental  derating
       will overwrite any existing derate value with the new value.

       When set to true, the successive application of the incremental derates
       will be accumulated into a final derate value.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

